org.galiosten.calculator.operation

Class Identity

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.galiosten.calculator.operation.Operation
      • org.galiosten.calculator.operation.Identity

  • public class Identity
extends Operation
    The Identity operation is a special case operation that models single Integer values in a way that can be evaluated as any other model. Unlike binary or ternary operations, the Identity operation stores the value directly, although it can be constructed from the results of evaluating other operations.
